manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: How does this t-shirt fit? Our Basic Tee fits true to size. It has a flattering fit that hugs your arms and chest, while hiding your dad bod. It elevates your look and looks great on most builds. What size should I order? We recommend reviewing the measurements in our size chart to choose the perfect tee shirt. What is the fabric composition? Our t-shirt is made with the perfect blend that's incredibly soft, lightweight, and breathable. Fabric Composition: 60% Combed Cotton 40% Polyester Are there specific care instructions? This men's tee is machine washable. We recommend to turn inside out and machine wash cold with like colors. Tumble dry on low. Do not iron, bleach or dry clean. What occasions is this shirt suitable for? This men's t shirt is perfect for casual everyday wear, dressing up, date night, working from home, layering with your outfit, outdoor activities, travel, and as lounge wear.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Everyone in review about fit absolutely correct. These shirts fit the best. I am 6 feet tall if my posture is good and 175 pounds. I ordered large. Definitely getting more of these. Material is light and soft. I like that there is no logo or pockets although their logo shirt still looks good. Nailed it for my preference.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice fitted tees for those who are in-shape, but not six-pack in-shape
reviews.reviewText: I'm in my 40's but do lift regularly while also enjoying food and wine regularly. I wanted nice, soft t-shirts that were fitted up top without being skin-tight and clingy, but with a middle that was just a little relaxed so as to not cling to my less-than-washboard abs. These shirts fit the bill. Super soft, nice cut, they fit up top they way I wanted them to, they're a little relaxed below the chest, and they seem to be wearing well through wash and dry cycles. I haven't noticed any shrinking washing them medium hot and drying on low. You can get less expensive shirts, but I think there's good value to these from a price/quality perspective.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just buy them!
reviews.reviewText: These T-shirts are great. Good quality and they fit great. I would wear them out in warm weather anywhere!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Zero regrets; my new favorite shirts!
reviews.reviewText: These shirts make all my other t shirts look like my wrong size. I absolutely LOVE these and the way they fit. I'm 6'2" and 180lbs and bought size XL. They hug my arms and are long! They looked a little bulky when I first got them but after a wash cycle they are perfect. Really good quality too. I'll definitely be buying from this store again.If you're not a taller guy, beware, they're a little long. But again, that's exactly what I was looking for.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought these shirts for my boyfriend who power lifts. Needless to say his arms are very strong and thick. These shirts were great because they allow for movement and aren’t thick or tight. He wears these shirts every day. He is 5’6”, 245 and I got him the XL which fit perfectly. I’ll be ordering him more once he wears these out!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The T-Shirt That Turned Me into a Magnet (and a Tech Icon Wannabe)
reviews.reviewText: If you’re scrolling through endless T-shirt options and wondering which one will change your life, stop right here. I stumbled upon this T-shirt brand, and let’s just say my wardrobe (and love life) has never been the same.Every time I slip one of these shirts on, my girlfriend suddenly forgets the concept of personal space – it’s like I’ve been dipped in boyfriend catnip! I’m not sure if it’s the fabric or the fit, but she can’t keep her hands off me. It’s gotten to the point where I’ve bought so many, I’m giving Mark Zuckerberg and Steve Jobs a run for their money in the signature look department.But seriously, these tees are fantastic – comfortable, stylish, and apparently woven with some sort of irresistible charm thread. If you’re looking to upgrade your T-shirt game to ‘tech mogul’ level and score some extra cuddles, this is your brand. Five stars, would recommend if you’re ready to be the center of attention (and affection)!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Very nice. My husband is very precise with his clothing and he loves these. They're soft and tapered, not like a tent (with larger sizes). Ordered more.
